Comment: pluto.princess said "( I don't expect any of you to read all this)

This 15 second video shows less than one percent of my 2014. I am not gonna say that I had a good year because I'd be lying. It was so shitty, if I'm honest. I had to see my brother's appearance fade away in the airport achingly slow, then it being transferred to computer screens with my other brother. I had to see myself change in some ways not completely positive. I had to find out that not everyone is nice and will like me. I felt alone constantly, even in the most crowded places, and it was fucking sad. I cried myself lots of times, but at those times, I realized, even on computer screens, my brothers are still here for me, my family and some friends are, too. I had discovered so many things, some bad, some good. I had met so many people, some fake, some real. And my point is, this year you'll be discovering more and more things, and you shouldn't expect them as all good ones, but you also shouldn't waste your time doing absolutely nothing, like I mostly did the past year. I am not going to say I regret because I really don't. I am not making any resolutions and promises because I'll break it January 3rd, and that's in like 2 days. And you shouldn't, too. You probably didn't even follow yours from 5 years ago... I don't know why I'm actually spending my time doing this, when I can be eating cake and just fall asleep. It's almost 3am for gods sake. Sigh. For the people that have been here for me, please stay with me, cause you're all I need. I know I sound like I am really drunk, but I am thankful you dealt with my existence. If you won't continue, then that's okay. Thank you anyway. I wish you a merry new year. Eat lots of cake, but save me some. <3"
